            ]
          },
          "body": {
            "text": "A large crag up to 40 metres high and around 500 metres long. Some early ascents were made in the 80s and 90s, while development started in 2011 by Simon Talltorp. Currently, there are about ten routes graded between 5 and 6. Great potential for first ascents exists for those who want to clean!",
